#89  The strain of being stranded in the 20th century begins to take its toll on the Legion members as two of them come to blows...and one leaves the team.

#90  Accidentally stirred out of catatonia by the telepathic powers of Saturn Girl, Dr. Psycho attacks the Legion. But this time, Saturn Girl becomes a psychic conduit for Psycho's evil mental powers, causing everyone around the Legionnaire to be caught up in the psychedelic madness.
